    	    			</div>
    	    							<h1 class="entry-title">How to Create an Injury-Free Workspace</h1>

<!--TYPECASTER-->
<div class="meta" style="height: 33px;">
       <div style="float: left;">
               by 	<a href="http://greatist.com/p/shana-lebowitz/">Shana Lebowitz</a>
 &middot; <abbr class='timeago' title='2012-08-28 12:08:14Z'>Tuesday, August 28th, 2012 08:08 am GMT -4</abbr> &middot; <a href="http://greatist.com/category/health/" title="View all posts in Health" rel="category tag">Health</a>       </div>

       <div style="clear: both;"></div>
</div>
<!--TYPECASTER-->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<!-- SimpleReach Slide Plugin Version: 0.7.5 -->
<script type='text/javascript' id='simplereach-slide-tag'>
